name: eros-modis-land-surface-temperature-2002-present
notes: The EROS Moderate Resolution Imaging Spectroradiometer (eMODIS) Aqua Land Surface Temperature (LST) product is similar to the Land Processes Distributed Active Archive Center (LP DAAC) 8-day product. It contains land surface temperature and emissivities retrieved from daily Aqua MODIS data at a spatial resolution of 1 km over global land surfaces under clear-sky conditions during a 10-day period. The eMODIS LST product is comprised of LST, emissivities estimated in bands 31 and 32, view angles, number of observations and quality assurance information.
